This is an Anroid app which is standalone.It has the basic functionality i.e a customer can signup and book a driver based his or her location(I have included only two to three sample locations).The location of driver when matches with customer a notification is sent to customer with respective driver details and driver is booked for the corresponding customer.

Features:

Customer signup 
Customer login
Driver signup
select Location 
Booking driver
Notification on assigning driver